# VHS tape — third README demo: fork lookup → spec drill-down.
# Render with:  vhs docs/assets/demo3.tape
# Output:       docs/assets/demo3.gif

Output docs/assets/demo3.gif

Set Theme "nord"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 940
Set Height 580
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 24
Set TypingSpeed 1ms
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "clear && python3 docs/assets/demo3.py"
Enter
Show
Sleep 20s
